From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Felix Hanau <felix@cloudflare.com>
Date: Sun, 9 Jul 2023 18:46:20 -0400
Subject: Enable V8 shared linkage

